Here is the comprehensive prompt you can copy and paste directly into Google Project IDX (or any Gemini-powered IDE).

This prompt is structured to **teach** the new agent how the framework works first, then instruct it to adapt it to your new idea while preserving the "premium" feel, animations, and video capabilities.

